body_html:
@PrinceP here is a pointer to the SpaceToBatchND kernel implementation https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/kernels/internal/reference/reference_ops.h#L3282 I made a recent change to add support for quantization for it.

I believe ResizeBilinear is supported now but we still need support for dilated depthwise conv. Thus i will mark this a duplicate of #20684.
